OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight rain clearing to a
OL,6,Fmix of sunny spells and blustery
OL,7,Fshowers on Tuesday. Some of the
OL,8,Fshowers potentially heavy with a risk
OL,9,Fof thunder. Warm in the sunny spells,
OL,10,Fbut breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers continuing through
OL,13,Fthe evening, but becoming lighter and
OL,14,Fgradually easing overnight. Staying
OL,15,Fbreezy, rather cloudy and mild across
OL,16,Fthe region.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy at first on
OL,19,FWednesday, but some brighter spells
OL,20,Fdeveloping at times. A few spots of
OL,21,Frain possible where the cloud thickens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
