OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FTurning drier, brighter and warmer
OL,7,Fthrough Thursday. Very warm on Friday
OL,8,Fand Saturday, although some thundery
OL,9,Fshowers are possible at times.
